                     <interp inst="t18280410-247-person1377" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer, and took the prisoner on the 8th of April; I found this ribbon and ring on her.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. He told me he had no money but some copper, and I saw none.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18280410-247-verdict1316" type="verdictDescription">
